<item>
            <title>[FLINK-29235] Update SnakeYAML to 1.31</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-29235</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Flink uses snakeyaml v1.27. &lt;br/&gt;
flink-shaded uses Jackson 2.12.4, which used snakeyaml v1.29&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Those version are vulnerable to CVE-2022-25857. Flink itself is not directly impacted by this CVE, but we should bump this to avoid false flags. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ref:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2022-25857&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2022-25857&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/flink/flink-shaded-jackson/2.12.4-15.0/flink-shaded-jackson-2.12.4-15.0.pom&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/flink/flink-shaded-jackson/2.12.4-15.0/flink-shaded-jackson-2.12.4-15.0.pom&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink-shaded/blob/master/flink-shaded-jackson-parent/flink-shaded-jackson-2/pom.xml#L73&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink-shaded/blob/master/flink-shaded-jackson-parent/flink-shaded-jackson-2/pom.xml#L73&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
